                            <comment id="13776447" author="lehmi" created="Tue, 24 Sep 2013 16:28:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;WOW, how did you find that small difference? That wasn&apos;t easy to see ...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, I fixed that in revision 1525939. PDFBox didn&apos;t use the given default width.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the report!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13776466" author="tilman" created="Tue, 24 Sep 2013 16:43:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, that was quick!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I found it through the efforts I described in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1695&quot; title=&quot;Improve pdfbox tests&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1695&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1695&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, i.e. I compare the rendering of &quot;old&quot; problem PDFs with saved renderings.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13872458" author="lehmi" created="Wed, 15 Jan 2014 19:20:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added the changes to the 1.8 branch in revision 1558531&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
